Sentencas: Y3+ and Ca2+ co-doped Ce0.8+xY0.2-2xCaxO1.9 (x = 0-0.1) electrolyte powders for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells were prepared by a low-temperature combustion synthesis method.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of Y3+ and Ca2+ co-doped ceria electrolyte materials for ITSOFC

Sentencas: The burnt powders had good sinterability and the relative densities of these sintered bodies were over 95% at 1350 degrees C for 4 h.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of Y3+ and Ca2+ co-doped ceria electrolyte materials for ITSOFC

Sentencas: The electrical property of Ce0.8+xY0.2-2xCaxO1.9 was studied by the impedance spectra analysis in the temperature range of 300-700 degrees C.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of Y3+ and Ca2+ co-doped ceria electrolyte materials for ITSOFC

Sentencas: The results displayed that the conductivity of the co-doped electrolytes was higher and the activation energy was lower compared with the singly doped ceria with the same oxygen vacancy concentration.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of Y3+ and Ca2+ co-doped ceria electrolyte materials for ITSOFC

Sentencas: The grain and the grain boundary conductivity of Ce0.8+xY0.2-2xCaxO1.9 (x = 0-0.1) electrolytes increased firstly and then decreased with increasing the Ca2+ concentration.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of Y3+ and Ca2+ co-doped ceria electrolyte materials for ITSOFC

Sentencas: The influence codoping on the electrical properties of the grain boundary was more apparent than that on the electrical properties of the grain.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of Y3+ and Ca2+ co-doped ceria electrolyte materials for ITSOFC

Sentencas: The influence mechanism of co-doping on the electrical properties of the grain and grain boundary was analyzed.
Titulo: Preparation and properties of Y3+ and Ca2+ co-doped ceria electrolyte materials for ITSOFC
